      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph props="autonumber">1852.216-75</ph> Payment of fixed fee.</title>
      <conbody>
         <p xtrc="P">As prescribed in <xref outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                  class="- topic/xref "
                  base="Section_1816_307_70_T48_6041815213"
                  href="Section_1816_307_70_T48_6041815213.dita#Section_1816_307_70_T48_6041815213">1816.307-70</xref>(c), insert the following clause:
</p>
                                    <p xtrc="HD1">Payment of Fixed Fee (DEC 1988)
</p>
                                    <p xtrc="P">The fixed fee shall be paid in monthly installments based upon the percentage of completion of work as determined by the Contracting Officer.</p>
                                 <p xtrc="HD3">(End of clause)
</p>
